10th St Explanation Meet Up
Dustin Moskovitz was invited
Come hang out at 10th St and learn of what we are trying to do now. We have spent the past month meeting with people and talking of the future of 10th St and think now we have come up with a legal good sustainable way to keep the place going so that everyone can still use it for events and whatnot. Come by and have a beer and sit around and hear and talk of what we are planning. Also if anyone wants to come by early because they are attending another event that evening we will be there from about 5 on preparing.
